Commenting on the post-Resurrection appearances of Jesus, Fredriksen said,I know in their own terms what they saw was the raised Jesus.
I’m not saying that they really did see the raised Jesus.
That Jesus appeared to more than 500 men and women at the same time is a truly remarkable claim.
Convincing HoratioThe extraordinary nature of Jesus’ resurrection reminds me of my favorite scene in Shakespeare’s Hamlet.
Encourage your skeptical friends not to stop at “I don’t know.” Give the risen Jesus welcome.